{"tid":759343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老真係好撚痴線 明知冇位都逼入lift","createTime":"2018-07-28T13:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T07:46:09.000Z","uid":184220,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"baabd2bb0b8490ac28a2f052cfd1fae8d7b46d2e","tid":759343,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"去完旅行拖住個喼搭機鐵。<br />\n我同幾個友人加三個大陸人入左lift，<br />\n每個人都拖住個喼部lift就冇哂位，<br />\n點知幾個廢老想衝入黎，<br />\n一路鳩叫「入面仲有位呀入啦！佢地都唔肯入！」<br />\n仲以為我地全部係支那人用蝗語講「進去進去有位子」<br />\n起勢咁撞我入lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗屌有電梯唔撚搭？<br />\n緊守關口既我就務求加劇中港紛爭，用支那話大叫<br />\n「別推啦，沒位子啊，草你媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」<br />\n再一手推開個廢老呀嬸出lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架lift一上去我居高臨下咁對住佢恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到佢指撚住我黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2bda167a0f50ee377ab094077b24abb793b8bb","tid":759343,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3313d3efd6ecce3bf4dadac83a192663f481cc","tid":759343,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6373f855d91e1a2807a698578048f4a157ea76","tid":759343,"uid":75935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"完全冇人理咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769481006b15a5505ccf3264524bc407927eda64","tid":759343,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"屌你地 咁撚英勇都冇人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96712470edec310b7e102e7711a8bfd17cf7082e","tid":759343,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:59:55.000Z","msg":"若然屬實，樓主或成最大贏家！"},{"pid":"ce566a8d9657b2e3ea1560d3143b871acf46d419","tid":759343,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9effff892adc268e52c1cca623a305c6d09388","tid":759343,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}